---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn the story behind CC's Cake Pops – handcrafted with love in Northwood, Ohio.">
  <main class="about-page">

    <!-- Hero split: photo + intro -->
    <section class="about-hero container">
      <div class="about-photo">
        <!-- Replace /about-photo.jpg with your actual photo in public/ -->
        <img src="/about-photo.jpg" alt="CC's Cake Pops – About Us" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'" />
        <div class="photo-placeholder">
          <span>🍭</span>
          <p>Add your photo to<br/><code>public/about-photo.jpg</code></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-intro">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>
        <h1>About CC's Cake Pops</h1>
        <hr class="dashed-divider" />
        <p>
          Hi, I'm CC, a cake pop maker based in Northwood, Ohio with a passion for
          turning simple celebrations into sweet memories. What started as a hobby in my
          kitchen has grown into something I'm truly proud to share with our community.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every cake pop I make is handcrafted from scratch, baked, dipped, and decorated
          with care. No shortcuts, no mass production. Just small batches made with love
          for people who deserve something special.
        </p>
        <div class="about-actions">
          <a href="/order" class="btn">Place an Order</a>
          <a href="/gallery" class="btn btn-outline">View Gallery</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Full story section -->
    <section class="about-story">
      <div class="container story-inner">
        <h2>How It All Started</h2>
        <hr class="dashed-divider" />
        <div class="story-body">
          <p>
            It all started with a birthday party and a batch of cake pops that didn't
            look quite right, but tasted absolutely amazing. Friends kept asking where
            I bought them, and when I told them I made them myself, the requests started
            rolling in.
          </p>
          <p>
            I spent months perfecting my recipes, experimenting with flavors, coatings,
            and decorating techniques. I took every custom order as a chance to learn
            something new. Weddings, baby showers, holidays, corporate events, each one
            pushed me to level up my craft.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, CC's Cake Pops serves families and businesses across Northwest Ohio.
            Whether you need a dozen pops for a small gathering or a full spread for a
            major event, I bring the same attention to detail and genuine love for the
            craft to every single order.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="about-cta">
      <div class="container cta-inner">
        <div>
          <h2>Ready to order?</h2>
          <p>Browse the gallery for inspiration or jump straight to placing your order.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href="/gallery" class="btn btn-outline">View Gallery</a>
          <a href="/order" class="btn">Order Now</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page { padding-bottom: 5rem; }

  /* Hero split */
  .about-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .about-photo {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(232,25,139,0.1);
  }

  .about-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .photo-placeholder {
    display: none;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-surface-soft) 0%, #fce4ef 100%);
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    min-height: 400px;
  }

  .photo-placeholder span { font-size: 4rem; }
  .photo-placeholder p { color: var(--color-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; }
  .photo-placeholder code {
    background: var(--color-border-soft);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about-intro .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .about-intro h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .dashed-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 2px dashed var(--color-border);
    opacity: 0.65;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-intro p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
  }

  /* Story section */
  .about-story {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .story-inner h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .story-body {
    columns: 2;
    column-gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .story-body p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    break-inside: avoid;
  }

  /* Values */
  .about-values { padding: 4.5rem 0; }

  .about-values h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(210px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(232,25,139,0.08);
  }

  .value-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.85rem; }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.87rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .about-cta {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    background: var(--color-surface-soft);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .about-cta h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .about-cta p { color: var(--color-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; flex-shrink: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .story-body { columns: 1; }
    .cta-inner { text-align: center; justify-content: center; }
    .cta-actions { justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
